                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">Zä-Wäldä Maryam is mentioned as the commissioner of the Ms. in the subscriptio on fol. 208r and in some supplication formulas (e.g., fols. 160va, 160vb, 161rc, 162rc, 183rc, 197rc, 197va) in the final part of the Ms. In the supplication on fol. 160va, he is mentioned together with "the children of this church" (däqiqä zatti betä krǝstiyan).&#xD;
